{"tid":1627833,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全新文宣誕生！香港人 反抗！ 廣傳！","createTime":"2019-10-05T18:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:11:25.000Z","uid":148317,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"214903f883fafc6e77f815340f6d857aad4e2f92","tid":1627833,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:10:38.000Z","msg":"代友post:<br />\n琴日個朋友設計左半日文宣，佢見到7婆實行幪面法。所以將主角帶上V煞面具，而手握黃遮。<br />\n<br />\n我問佢點解要用v煞，而唔用其他？<br />\n佢答我v煞個心態好值得去學習。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gRKNphb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgRKNphb.png&h=ee163be0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/odq1tJS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fodq1tJS.png&h=059c36c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家會用張文宣啦，話曬個朋友設計左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後朋友叫我同大家講:「7婆用緊急法，香港人驚嘅話，就中曬7婆個計劃」佢仲講左句英文「People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2273bc4688db4ced65f9bb7a0def6208009fffd6","tid":1627833,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:12:00.000Z","msg":"入黎 支持下我朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40512f8b6bbd278d3064f45b57d3c65f7304b974","tid":1627833,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"544fdf03bf3da41c0e79d48bbaa6012f2f7b6a60","tid":1627833,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:12:35.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"27b4159ba87dadd1748a64f9e0c4ed5cb5dfa4b3","tid":1627833,"uid":249243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:12:41.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"da4e3583b7cfe8bf69519216b80d6e2e75a36e66","tid":1627833,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime